extends layout
block content
  h1= title
  p.lead Full CRUD via web forms — add students, change their programme, delete them.
  .row.mt-4
    .col-md-6
      .card.mb-3
        .card-body
          h5.card-title View Students
          a.btn.btn-primary(href='/students') Go to Students
    .col-md-6
      .card.mb-3
        .card-body
          h5.card-title Add a Student
          a.btn.btn-success(href='/students/add') Add Student
  .alert.alert-info.mt-2
    strong New in Lab 10:
    |  Students can be added via a form. Their programme can be changed with an edit form. Uses model.insert() and model.updateById().
